snippet: FIFA says about 1,400 people will have to change their tickets less than a week before the World Cup begins because they were handed out before work at the stadiums was completed....

headline.print_headline: More Than 1,300 Fans Notified of Ticket Changes
headline.main: More Than 1,300 Fans Notified of Ticket Changes

lead_paragraph: FIFA says about 1,400 people will have to change their tickets less than a week before the World Cup begins because they were handed out before work at the stadiums was completed.
